[Cite as 03105/2003 Case Announcements, 2003-Ohio-904.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

March 5, 2003

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2001-1956. Citizen Power, Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 00-2469-EL-UNC. On motions to dismiss. Motions to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton and O’Connor, JJ., concur. Cook, J., not participating.
